@@ -78,6 +78,8 @@ The payload and sidecar paths are protected from ordinary write, append, rename,
 
 This naming hardening prevents collision-driven quarantine denial; it does not claim content-addressed storage against a full SHA-256 collision.
 
+User-visible shell and ring-3 reads of `/quarantine/*` are denied independently of current ZMID signatures and require persistent `READ-BLOCK` evidence. Only dedicated trusted quarantine management and rollback paths use raw reads.
+
